{
  "stem": "18960.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And whether they-- they were-- whether they were herding them to Janowska or to extermination camp, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Anyway, this was my greetings in Lwow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And it felt very uncomfortable.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I went to a barber shop, because somehow I thought my eyebrows may give me away.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I have too thick of eyebrows.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "So I went to the barber shop to get a haircut and a shave.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And I told the barber he should thin out my eyebrows.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "He looked a little, let's see, funny at me, but he-- he didn't suspect me that I'm a Jew.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "But he thinned them out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And then I went to the railroad station in-- in-- with Voloshyn, together.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Then there was the gathering of all these workers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And they had to go to a public bath.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Before they boarded, you had to get a piece of paper that you participated in the public bath, because the Germans were afraid to [INAUDIBLE] epidemics and so forth.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "I didn't-- I wasn't anxious to go to the public bath, because I know if I go to that public bath and they see me that I am circumcised, I give myself away right away, because in Europe, only Jews were-- were circumcised.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "The general population was not circumcised-- not like in America.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "So this was one-- one thing to-- it could-- could have given me away immediately.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I said to this fellow Voloshyn, you know, you go to bath with them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, you will be coming back [INAUDIBLE] I'll sneak into your group.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'll take my attache case.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I'll go into the-- to railway station.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that's what happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was staying-- I was staying inside.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They went.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
